title: They See Me Trollblin
description: The tiny Kotassians hire the Warriors to exterminate two humongous Trollblins that have invaded their village, but it turns out that the Trollblins are actually nice guys and the Warriors switch sides to protect them in a Kotassiam/Trollblin War!

title: UG Christmas Special
description: Santa and Uncle Grandpa must work through their personal differences order to save Christmas.

title: Welcome to Zombozo-Zone!
description: During medieval times, Team Tennyson must fight to remember that they're not in the past at all, but actually at a Renaissance-esque faire, where "King Zombozo" has hypnotized its guests into thinking they live in the past!

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Random Acts of Memory
description: The Warriors learn that Nohyas has been using a Selective Memory Magisword to erase select interactions with Prohyas' bizarre doppelganger their entire lives, so their new mission: take back that sword!

title: Haunted House/Two of a Kind
description: Haunted House: Rumor has it that there's a haunted building in Los Volmos, and the Awesome Brawlers are on the case! Who doesn't like a good ghost hunt, plus capturing a ghost on camera should make Awesome Brawlers' next video a huge success!/Two of a Kind: Veronica Venegas is doing a special report on the Awesome brawlers own: Lightening! The special report takes a back seat when Lightening is challenged to a brawl. Lightening uses this brawl the perfect opportunity to rollout his new Bakugan partner: Tretorous.

title: La identidad de carton
description: Craig y sus amigos se topan con un refugio subterráneo hecho de cartón debajo del bosque.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Second Christmas
description: The Titans trick Starfire into believing in second Christmas with second Santa.

title: Whacky Jaxxyz
description: Cuando Whacky Jaxxyz, el nuevo juego de moda, llega a Lakewoood, KO se despide de sus tarjetas de poder.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: La Formula de Manzana
description: Manzana necesita encontrar una fórmula divertida que le permita conseguir un papel cómico en una película.

title: The End of the Universe I Part 1
description: Starscream's fate at the hands of the Quintessons is revealed as he returns a three-headed Judge!

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: Contrabandistas de Azucar
description: Craig, Kelsey y JP se convierten en contrabandistas para llevarle dulces a niños necesitados.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Three Gems and a Baby
description: Greg tells Steven the story of his first winter with Steven.

title: Scary Tales 2
description: It's Halloween again and the gang is desperately trying to tell the scariest story to a couple of trick or treaters. Each of the characters takes turns adding onto the last story, going through a haunted glove to a haunted action figure to haunted everything, and even a spooky song! None work in scaring the kids when suddenly a full scale alien invasion happens right before their eyes! Still, the trick or treaters are unimpressed until Richard takes the story stage and delivers a story no kid wants to hear- instead of candy, the trick or treaters would get granola bars! The kids, and Puppycorn, run away screaming.

title: Too Cool
description: Puppycorn needs a lesson in how to be cool. The gang is more than happy to teach him, until his coolness unexpectedly freezes the whole kingdom.

title: The Vampire Strikes Back
description: Ben, Rook, and Rad Dudesman come face to face with the evil Lord Transyl, a vampire-like alien who can make anyone his loyal slave! (Introducing new Ben alien, Whampire.)

title: The Bad Guy Busters
description: Izzy wants to play a superhero game and is willing to do whatever it takes to get the others to see it through.

title: Hard Times in Silicon City
description: Mega Man must stop Blasto Woman from plundering the Museum of the Hard Age and its cache of military grade weaponry.

title: La princesa de jade
description: A raíz de un cruel ataque al Palacio, Los Hijos de Garmadon roban la segunda Máscara Oni, y los ninjas invitan a la Princesa Real, Harumi, a su improvisada familia.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Bienvenido a la Zona Zombozo
description: Durante tiempos medievales, el equipo Tennyson debe esforzarse por recordar que no están en el pasado, sino en una feria renacentista, idonde el "Rey Zombozo" ha hipnotizado a sus invitados para que crean que viven en el pasado!

title: Elect to Decline
description: Noville wants to impress Vambre with a new Magisword from the Cave of Stuff, but the Cave Weirdos are in election mode and horrible smear campaigning is making Noville's simple task impossible!

title: The More You Moe, the Moe You Know
description: Moe visits the tree house with a special birthday surprise for BMO. While BMO's mission stands on the brink of disaster, Finn & Jake host a strange guest.

title: Sidekick Scouts
description: KO gets more than he bargained for when he gets a sidekick.

title: Mas del canal de todos
description: A través de otra sesión de navegación por Internet, vemos más videos subidos por los Osos y sus amigos.

title: Fragments
description: Steven heads to the woods to train with a powerful mentor.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: El chillido de hombre muerto
description: La casi desaparición de Zane a manos del Señor "E" obliga a los ninjas a huir a bordo del Bounty, donde descubren que una tramisión que Zane interceptó puede revelar la ubicación oculta del "Silencioso".
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Tales from the Omnitrix
description: Team Tennyson trade campfire stories in an anthology-style series that pits Ben against his archrival, Kevin 11, and teaches our hero the power of imagination.

title: Lad & Logic
description: KO learns the story of how Mr. Logic came to the plaza.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sleepover at JP's
description: JP invites his friends over for a sleepover, but it happens to be on the night of a huge game of Flashlight Tag in the Creek!

title: My Fair Achi
description: V&V enter Achi in a dog show competition to win a golden trophy, but their overbearing ways drive Achi to the edge.

title: Bloqueo de Tránsito
description: Cuando un paso elevado colapsa sobre la autopista, el equipo Tennyson queda varado en un embotellamiento junto con Simon Sez y familia. Pero cuando Ben y Simon se alían para enfrentar juntos al atasco, Simon solo consigue que las cosas sean mucho, pero mucho peores.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Queen of the Munce
description: Jay, Nya and Lloyd are led deep into the Mines of Shintaro by Murt, who brings them back to the Munce "Home- Cave" - a settlement deep in the mountain. There, complications arise when they meet the Munce Queen, Murtessa, who takes a liking to Jay.

title: Unfriendly Competition
description: Aki must set aside a petty rivalry with Bert Wily in order to stop Chemistry Man from wreaking havoc at Silicon Central's Field Day.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: The Bakugan Battle League/The Ancient Elder
description: The Bakugan Battle League: Benton Dusk is in the process of renovating a state of the art Bakugan Brawling stadium. When it comes to brawling, who better to test out the new arena than the Awesome Brawlers!/The Ancient Elder: Dan finds a new baku-bud in Gillitar. Well "bud" may be too strong a word, Dan and gang quickly learn that Gillator has a few "quirks" that keep him from fitting in with the rest of the Awesome Brawler's Bakugan.

title: The Judge Part 1
description: The Quintesson Judge and his forces assault Iaconus while Optimus and Megatron lead a strike team into the Quintesson ship.

title: Snow Month
description: After a snow day saves Blossom from having to face a boy who's asked her out, she decides to use her ice breath to keep it going even if that means plunging Townsville into eternal winter complete with monstrous yetis!

title: Everything's Fine
description: Steven insists that everything is fine.

title: The Night
description: As night falls in Elmore, the Moon takes us on a tour through the various dreams and nightmares of the town's slumbering inhabitants. Each character's dream shows us their innermost desires, their greatest fears or just how plain weird they are.

title: Costume Crisis
description: Uncle Grandpa makes improvements to a kid's Halloween costume.

title: The Skull Sorcerer
description: Separated from the others, Cole must trust his instincts and make the right choices to find his way to the surface to alert King Vangelis of the dangerous Skull Sorcerer.

title: 'Twas the Fight Before Christmas
description: When Princess Morbucks tries to ruin Christmas for the children of the world, the Powerpuff Girls must save the day.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Animal Day
description: Clarence feels the call of the wild - and decides to live a new life, free of the hustle and bustle of the modern world. Recruiting a few friends, Clarence sets out to find a new place to live his feral life, but quickly realizes he lacks some basic survival skills.

title: Chill Out
description: Uncle Grandpa takes a kid to the North Pole for an epic snowball battle.

title: The End of the Universe II Part 1
description: Windblade battles the Sharkticons to regain entry into Iaconus.

title: Gobble Head
description: Chef accidentally cooks up a killer cyborg turkey in a failed attempt to get the kids to appreciate him on Appreciation Day.

title: No Day Like Snow Day
description: When a blizzard hits the town, Master Frown tries to ruin everyone's fun by pretending to be a magical snowman! But when he gets frozen inside, Master Frown must worry less about ruining everyone's good time and instead not turning into a Frown-sicle, while he's forced to experience the joys of the holiday season!

title: Snarf's Day Off
description: Hey everyone, it's Snarf's monthly day off! That's right, this episode follows Snarf as he leaves Cats' Lair to get a needed vacation, by transforming into a normal cat and hanging out with a nice old lady on a farm! But his relaxing day is threatened when Snarf and the nice old lady cross paths with Mumm-Ra!

title: The Christmas Special
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to destroy a gift for Santa to save Christmas.

title: The Judge Part 2
description: Megatron and Optimus's strike team faces off against the Scientist while the Autobot and Decepticon defenders of Iaconus desperately keep the all-powerful Judge distracted.

title: Un dia nevado
description: Cuando una tormenta de nieve llega a la ciudad, Master Frown trata de arruinar la diversión de todos fingiendo ser un muñeco de nieve mágico. Pero cuando se congela por dentro, Master Frown debe preocuparse menos por arruinar la diversión de todos y más por no convertirse en un témpano malhumorado, imientras se ve obligado a experimentar la alegría de la temporada navideña!

title: Holly Jolly Secrets Part 2
description: Finn and Jake continue to explore the world of old Christmas specials while the Ice King fumes.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Perfect Tree
description: Chloe and Ice Bear drive up north to find the perfect Christmas tree. Meanwhile, Grizz and Panda are in charge of decorating Chloe's house.

title: Merry Christmas Mordecai
description: Mordecai has to get through a Christmas party with C.J. without messing everything up.

title: The End of the Universe I Part 2
description: Judge Starscream interrogates his Cybetronian prisoners while Optimus, Bee, and Wheeljack try to get back through the Multiverse Bridge.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Dead Man's Squall
description: Zane's near demise at the hands of Mr. E forces the ninja to flee aboard the Bounty, where they discover that a transmission Zane intercepted may reveal the hidden location of the Quiet One.

title: Mi Villana Familia
description: KO, Rad y Enid se sienten confundidos cuando descubren que los villanos están más interesados en enfrentarse entre sí que en enfrentarlos a ellos.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Appleoni
description: Apple and Onion want credit for creating a new dance craze.

title: Ayudantes Scouts
description: KO obtiene más de lo que esperaba cuando consigue su propio ayudante.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Collect This
description: Ben finally meets the ones responsible for his intergalactic TV show, and the actor who makes Ben 10 more famous than Ben himself!

title: El Arbol Perfecto
description: Chloe y Polar conducen hacia el norte para encontrar el árbol de Navidad perfecto. Mientras tanto, Pardo y Panda quedan a cargo de la decoración de la casa de Chloe.

title: Return of Thermometron 9000
description: During a brutal heatwave, Axel and his team must track down Thermometron 9000, stolen by Ice Crusher for two purposes - to keep his hockey rink from melting and to bait the good toys into a rematch!

title: Christmas Parties
description: The Bears have been invited to all their friends' Christmas parties. In an effort to have time to crash Nom Nom's huge star-studded bash, the Bears first try to make quick stops at all their friends' parties throughout the night.

title: Project Ray Way
description: When Raymond starts his own fashion line, Rad and Drupe decide to make something even better.

title: Hideous Hound
description: Prohyas pets an unsightly stray dog, and from that moment on the poor pooch appears on a variety of Warrior missions, driving Vambre and Vambre's brain insane!

title: I Am My Monster
description: Everything is not fine.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Gift
description: The girls must replace the Professor's Christmas present on Christmas Eve.

title: Ener-G-Shoes
description: When Vic uses trickery to buy a pair of super cool sneakers from Maria Teresa's yard sale, the shoes try to walk him to his demise as punishment.

title: Old Lady Bodyguard
description: After being "bought" at a charity auction, Hawkodile is forced to spend the day as Old Lady Edith's personal bodyguard.

title: Los Caza Chicos Malos
description: Izzqy quiere jugar un juego de superhéroes y está dispuesta a hacer lo que sea por ello.

title: Snake Jaguar
description: In order to join the Sons of Garmadon, Zane (aka Snake Jaguar) participates in a deadly motorcycle initiation race.

title: Encantadas
description: Durante una comida familiar en un campamento forestal, Charmcaster usa su magia para cambiar de lugar con Gwen, pero cuando Ben descubre a "Charmcaster" husmeando, ataca, sin darse cuenta de que en realidad es su hechizada prima.

title: Midnight at the Mayor's Mansion
description: When the Mayor's mansion is stalked by a vicious, ghostly monster, he calls the Powerpuff Girls for help.

title: Guar serpiente
description: Para unirse a Los Hijos de Garmadon, Zane (alias Jaguar Serpiente) participa en una carrera de iniciación mortal de motocicletas.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: Secret Santa
description: When Uncle Grandpa and the crew all have the same popular and hard-to-find gift in mine for their Secret Santa, their nice Christmas shopping trip to the mall turns into a crazy competition.

title: Christmas in Space
description: The guys celebrate their first Christmas in space by opening presents, eating peppermint bark and telling Christmas stories. Benson wants the stories to be more Christmas-y but the guys keep adding scary elements, which only infuriate their boss.

title: River of Gold
description: Apple & Onion try to finish a story before the book disappears forever.

title: Merry Christmas
description: When the Rustbucket's A/C goes on the fritz in the middle of the desert, Ben, Max and Gwen take refuge at Holiday Village, an over the top Christmas theme park that seems to appear out of nowhere. The place is run by an evil entity known as Mr. Jingles, who takes Max prisoner because he believes Max is Santa! It's up to Ben and Gwen to free Max and break the spell Mr. Jingles has cast on Holiday Village, freeing others who've been trapped their for years and releasing the theme park.

title: Holly Jolly Secrets Part 1
description: Finn and Jake continue to explore the world of old Christmas specials while the Ice King fumes.

title: Lista de Traviesos
description: Es Nochebuena y Brock está emocionado por la visita de Santa Claus. Mientras se prepara para que Master Frown le lea un cuento para dormir, Unikitty y la banda irrumpen en su casa. Están ahí para evitar que Master Frown arruine más Navidades. Frown se declara inocente, pero Unikitty y la banda cuentan las historias de las Navidades pasadas que ya arruinó. ¿Frown probará su inocencia o se pondrá a la cabeza de la lista de los traviesos?

title: Homeworld Bound
description: Steven heads to the Diamonds for advice on how to control his new powers.

title: Log Date 7 15 2
description: Steven sneaks a listen to a friend's audio diary.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sugar Smugglers
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP become smugglers to sneak candy to kids in need.

title: Meet Tygra
description: The smartest Thundercat, Tygra. Tygra's mission is to make Lion-O a better leader. He might get around to it too, if he wasn't so busy cleaning up after the other Thundercats.

title: An American Benwolf in London
description: Ben and Rook are called to London England to investigate the Forever Knights' latest activities.

title: La Cucarachita
description: When Vic's beloved pet cockroach dies, Vic turns to Charlene's dark magic to bring her back to life.

title: The Guest
description: Vic & Val blame each other for eating all the food in the kitchen and making a huge mess! However, they soon discover that a ghost is actually to blame! They enlist the help of Achi to unlock the world of spirits among them and kick the ghost out of their house!

title: Just Like Robots
description: Axel and the team find themselves bested by Madcap when the baddie uses their digital devices to track their every move in combat, forcing our heroes to act unpredictably.

title: El joven y la logica
description: K.O. descubre cómo el Sr. Lógica llegó a la Plaza.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Bridge Out
description: After an overpass collapses on the highway, Team Tennyson is in a traffic jam along with Simon Sez and family. But when Ben and Simon team up to tackle the gridlock together, Simon only makes matters much, much worse.

title: Fright Wig
description: When the King cannot overcome his fears, he abuses having the Sheriff's Dept. on call.

title: Peluca de Terror
description: Cuando el rey no logra superar sus miedos, se abusa de la ventaja que le da tener al departamento del sheriff de guardia.

title: The Real Fall!
description: An entire episode chronicles the ninja's most bizarre adventure yet: in which Cole, Princess Vania and Master Wu fall down a seemingly endless tunnel, into the bowels of Shintaro Mountain.

title: OWW
description: When the kids discover Chef's past as a disgraced pro wrestler, they invite his old tag team partner to help put on a charity show. But is the big match about re-union or re-venge?!?

title: Rio de Oro
description: Manzana y Cebolla intentan terminar un cuento antes de que el libro desaparezca para siempre.

title: Pijamada en casa de JP
description: JP invita a sus amigos para una pijamada, pero resulta ser la misma noche que un gran juego con linternas en el Arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Beach Heads
description: After traveling to Tampa Beach, Florida, Team Tennyson hopes to get some much-needed rest & relaxation, but the tempests without a temper, the Weatherheads, have other plans that Ben must thwart: to build a new beach base!

title: Toddler Titans...Yay!
description: Control Freak thinks the Titans' humor is too juvenile for their time-slot, so he ages them down to a preschool show.

title: Aventuras Cuidando Ninos
description: Ben, Gwen y Max se encuentran con una familia que parece ser un reflejo de ellos. Pero cuando Max sale a caminar con su matriarca, Maxine, Ben se ve obligado a cuidar a Simon Sez, un malcriado con una mochila diseñada por Billy Billones, que lo convierte en un robot formidable.

title: La Limosna
description: Para ayudar a Panda a distraerse de sus problemas románticos, Pardo y Polar le regalan un paseo en limosina.

title: Abate and Switch
description: When the JLA tries to stop the Brothers Djinn, the ghoulish trio are able to direct spells on our heroes by saying their names forcing them to disguise themselves as each other in order to foil the spells.

title: Winter Forecast
description: Steven has to get Connie home before it snows.

title: Top of the Naughty List
description: It's Christmas Eve and Brock is excited for Santa to come and visit as he settles down for a bedtime story from Master Frown, Unikitty and gang burst in. They are there to stop Master Frown from ruining any more Christmases. Frown pleads innocent but Unikitty and the gang tell the stories of the past Christmases he has already ruined.  Will Frown prove his innocence or will he rocket to the top of the Naughty List?

title: Opposites Attract
description: Fire Man and Wave Man team up to evaporate the city's water supply, forcing Mega Man to team up with an ally of his own- Suna.

title: Kevin 11
description: After a big argument with Max, Ben rebels by going out on his own in the Big Apple and makes friends with Kevin 11, who has plans for the Omnitrix.

title: Tourist Trap
description: While messing with the World's Largest Rubberband Ball at a tourist trap, Ben accidently releases some mischievous electrical creatures.

title: Breaking Bliss
description: When Bliss struggles to control her powers an evil force arises to take advantage.

title: Election Day
description: Apple runs for Mayor.

title: The Limo
description: To help distract Panda from his girl problems, Grizz and Ice Bear treat him to a ride in a limo.

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Primera parte
description: En el episodio estreno de cuatro partes de la serie, seis chicas comunes y corrientes se conocen y descubren que tienen poderes extraordinarios. Deciden unir sus fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Creek Daycare
description: Craig and his sister, Jessica, try their hand at running the daycare at the Creek.

title: The Tunnel
description: After Clarence accidentally knocks Belson's new video game down a storm drain, Belson enters the large underground sewer tunnel to retrieve it. When Belson doesn't return, Clarence must decide whether or not to go in after him.

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: #FantasticBeastsAndHowToMindThem
description: Diana Prince receives a care package from home, and her pet-raising skills are soon put to the test when a mysterious egg hatches into a baby griffin.

title: La mascara del engano
description: Cuando un sindicato de criminals desconocido amenaza a la Familia Real, los ninjas son llamados de nuevo a la acción y deben proteger a la princesa real y un artefacto legendario que puede tener poderes sobrenaturales.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: More Everyone's Tube
description: Through another video browsing session online, we get more videos uploaded by the Bears and their friends.

title: Dungeon Party
description: Having survived their fall into the mountain, Cole, Wu and Princess Vania befriend a motley group of survivors, called the Lowly, and are told the story of how they too ended up at "Rock-Bottom."

title: Merry Moochmas
description: It's wintertime in Aberdale and Clarence is convinced his winter wish for snow in Arizona will come true! However, his classmate Belson along with his grumpy cousin Gary Mooch are a little tougher to convince.

title: Cabeza de Playa
description: Después de viajar a Tampa Beach, Florida, el equipo Tennyson espera poder descansar y relajarse, pero las tempestades sin temperamento, los Climáticos, tienen otros planes que Ben debe frustrar: iconstruir una nueva base en la playa!

title: Huggbees
description: The Brain teams up with The Lobe, so the Titans enlist the help of Freakazoid to stop them.

title: Sofa Cama
description: Cuando los Piratas del Cielo se infiltran en el cuartel general del sheriff, iponen en peligro a los héroes!

title: Mystery, Incorporeal
description: An old enemy emerges while Ben and Rook visit Kevin and Gwen at college.

title: The Jade Princess
description: In the wake of a vicious attack upon the palace, the Sons of Garmadon steal the second Oni Mask, and the ninja invite the royal princess, Harumi, into their makeshift family.

title: Baost in Show
description: When Bao Bao returns, and the King makes him his pet, Mao Mao must rescue his ex-partner.

title: Christmas Movies
description: On Christmas Eve, the Baby Bears defend a video store from getting robbed.

title: Snow Tubing
description: Rigby wants Eileen to go snow tubing.

title: Talent Show
description: Clarence throws a big talent show in his yard to showcase all the fun hidden talents of his friends. But when Brady claims he's talentless, Clarence sets out to prove that everyone has something special to share!

title: Rad Monster Party
description: Ben and Rook enlist the help of intergalactic smuggler Rad Dudesman to fly them through the Anur System, the home of the monstrous aliens!

title: Lords of Ghost Town
description: When V&V recruit a ghost to scare away a bully, they end up messing with the realm of the dead, which has disastrous consequences.

title: Lion-S
description: Lion-O and the other ThunderCats are thrilled to meet a brand new Thunderian: Lion-S! She's cool, good at fighting robots and, most importantly, thinks Lion-O and his Sword of Omens are really neat and interesting! Looks like the ThunderCats have a new best friend! Maybe even, a new ThunderCat?????

title: The True Meaning of Christmas
description: Fed up with never getting presents from Santa, the Titans head to the north pole to take themselves off the Naughty List by any means necessary.

title: Billy Billones
description: En Aspen, Colorado, Ben, Gwen y el abuelo Max van de excursión para encontrar al Olvideti. Pero cuando se encuentran con la pista artificial de esquí de Billy Billones, Ben debe luchar contra Billy con la ayuda del propio Olvideti.

title: Sleeper Sofa
description: When the Sky Pirates infiltrate Sheriff HQ, they put our heroes in danger!

title: Clayton
description: Darwin necesita encontrar una foto de Clayton para ponerla en la portada del anuario escolar... ipero comete el error de pedirle ayuda de Tobías, que está interesado en aparecer en la portada!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Meet The Thunderkittens
description: The Thunderkittens might be the youngest Thundercats, but Wilykit and Wilykat are a dynamic brother and sister duo! They'll help take down any foe, even if they don't really know what their own capsule weapons can do.

title: All in the Villainy
description: KO, Rad and Enid are confused to find the villains are more interested in battling each other than them.

title: The Lady and the Queen/The AB's Silver Screen Debut
description: The Lady and the Queen: China Riot finds a new Bakugan: Barbetra. But this buzzy new Bakugan is a bit timid on the battleground.
